’Ů@7a20f6ba22db066435e67db93de6aa56348441593c145dadb82e4d4898302d96ÚTitle: title: to csv
Path: Flags
Content:
``--separator, -s {string}``
: A character to separate columns, defaults to ','.
``--noheaders, -n``
: Do not output the columns names as the first row.
``--columns {list<string>}``
: The names (in order) of the columns to use.
’Ů@b213236abc91c5828a72397ef606838fa58bda41bef130724af3d11dcb41037bŮ`Title: title: to csv
Path: Input/output types:
Content:
